## Full-Stack-in-Django-Framework

This repository contains code examples of various workstations and features I was in charge of full-stack developing, committing, and maintaining to build a native cloud-based shop floor control (SFC) that is currently being deployed in multiple manufacturing plants (in North America and oversea) of a company in the [top 5 world largest manufacturing companies by revenue](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_largest_manufacturing_companies_by_revenue#:~:text=%20%20%20%20No.%20%20%20,%20South%20Korea%20%2036%20more%20rows%20). The shop floor management application is used to track the progress of assembly lines, test the raw components as well as finished products, and report the status of work of manufacturing plants, and is tailored to the needs of different client's projects (Amazon, Facebook, Microsoft, Seagate)
